{"id":134,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":134,"title":"D&C 130","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 130"],[".studyIntro",["i","Items of instruction given by Joseph Smith the Prophet, at Ramus, Illinois, April 2, 1843."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.1-3"},"1–3"],", The Father and the Son may appear personally to men;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.4-7"},"4–7"],", Angels reside in a celestial sphere;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.8-9"},"8–9"],", The celestial earth will be a great Urim and Thummim;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.10-11"},"10–11"],", A white stone is given to all who enter the celestial world;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.12-17"},"12–17"],", The time of the Second Coming is withheld from the Prophet;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.18-19"},"18–19"],", Intelligence gained in this life rises with us in the Resurrection;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.20-21"},"20–21"],", All blessings come by obedience to law;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.22-23"},"22–23"],", The Father and the Son have bodies of flesh and bones."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.1","order":"06.05.130.16085"},["b","1"],"When the Savior shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"appear"],"we shall see him as he is. We shall see that he is a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"man"],"like ourselves."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.2","order":"06.05.130.16086"},["b","2"],"And that same",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"sociality"],"which exists among us here will exist among us there, only it will be coupled with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"eternal glory"],", which glory we do not now enjoy."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.3","order":"06.05.130.16087"},["b","3"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/14.23"},"John 14:23"],"—The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"appearing"],"of the Father and the Son, in that verse, is a personal",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"appearance"],"; and the idea that the Father and the Son",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"dwell"],"in a man’s heart is an old sectarian notion, and is false."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.4","order":"06.05.130.16088"},["b","4"],"In answer to the question—Is not the reckoning of God’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"time"],", angel’s time, prophet’s time, and man’s time, according to the planet on which they reside?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.5","order":"06.05.130.16089"},["b","5"],"I answer, Yes. But there are no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"angels"],"who",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"minister"],"to this earth but those who do belong or have belonged to it."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.6","order":"06.05.130.16090"},["b","6"],"The angels do not reside on a planet like this earth;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.7","order":"06.05.130.16091"},["b","7"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"they"],"reside in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"presence"],"of God, on a globe",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"like"],"a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"sea"],"of glass and",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_7e"},"fire"],", where all things for their glory are manifest, past, present, and future, and are continually before the Lord."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.8","order":"06.05.130.16092"},["b","8"],"The place where God resides is a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Urim and Thummim"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.9","order":"06.05.130.16093"},["b","9"],"This",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"earth"],", in its",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"sanctified"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"immortal"],"state, will be made like unto",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"crystal"],"and will be a Urim and Thummim to the inhabitants who dwell thereon, whereby all things pertaining to an inferior kingdom, or all kingdoms of a lower order, will be manifest to those who dwell on it; and this earth will be",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_9e"},"Christ’s"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.10","order":"06.05.130.16094"},["b","10"],"Then the white",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"stone"],"mentioned in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/2.17"},"Revelation 2:17"],", will become a Urim and Thummim to each individual who receives one, whereby things pertaining to a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"higher"],"order of kingdoms will be made known;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.11","order":"06.05.130.16095"},["b","11"],"And a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"white stone"],"is given to each of those who come into the celestial kingdom, whereon is a new",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"name"],"written, which no man knoweth save he that receiveth it. The new name is the key word."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.12","order":"06.05.130.16096"},["b","12"],"I prophesy, in the name of the Lord God, that the commencement of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"difficulties"],"which will cause much bloodshed previous to the coming of the Son of Man will be in South Carolina."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.13","order":"06.05.130.16097"},["b","13"],"It may probably arise through the slave question. This a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"voice"],"declared to me, while I was praying earnestly on the subject, December 25th, 1832."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.14","order":"06.05.130.16098"},["b","14"],"I was once praying very earnestly to know the time of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"coming"],"of the Son of Man, when I heard a voice repeat the following:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.15","order":"06.05.130.16099"},["b","15"],"Joseph, my son, if thou livest until thou art eighty-five years old, thou shalt see the face of the Son of Man; therefore",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"let"],"this suffice, and trouble me no more on this matter."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.16","order":"06.05.130.16100"},["b","16"],"I was left thus, without being able to decide whether this coming referred to the beginning of the millennium or to some previous appearing, or whether I should die and thus see his face."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.17","order":"06.05.130.16101"},["b","17"],"I believe the coming of the Son of Man will not be any sooner than that time."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.18","order":"06.05.130.16102"},["b","18"],"Whatever principle of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"intelligence"],"we attain unto in this life, it will rise with us in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.19","order":"06.05.130.16103"},["b","19"],"And if a person gains more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"knowledge"],"and intelligence in this life through his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"diligence"],"and obedience than another, he will have so much the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"advantage"],"in the world to come."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.20","order":"06.05.130.16104"},["b","20"],"There is a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"law"],", irrevocably decreed in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"heaven"],"before the foundations of this world, upon which all",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"blessings"],"are predicated—"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.21","order":"06.05.130.16105"},["b","21"],"And when we obtain any",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"blessing"],"from God, it is by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"obedience"],"to that law upon which it is predicated."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.22","order":"06.05.130.16106"},["b","22"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Father"],"has a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"body"],"of flesh and bones as tangible as man’s; the Son also; but the Holy Ghost has not a body of flesh and bones, but is a personage of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"Spirit"],". Were it not so, the Holy Ghost could not",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_22d"},"dwell"],"in us."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.23","order":"06.05.130.16107"},["b","23"],"A man may receive the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"Holy Ghost"],", and it may descend upon him and not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"tarry"],"with him."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.1a","order":"06.05.130.16108"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/3.2"},"1 Jn. 3:2"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.1b","order":"06.05.130.16110"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"},"TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-potential-to-become-like-heavenly-father"},"Man, Potential to Become like Heavenly Father"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.2a","order":"06.05.130.16112"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-eternal"},"TG Family, Eternal"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"Family, Love within"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-continuing-courtship-in"},"Marriage, Continuing Courtship in"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.2b","order":"06.05.130.16114"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/celestial-glory"},"TG Celestial Glory"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/eternal-life"},"Eternal Life"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.3a","order":"06.05.130.16116"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-privilege-of-seeing"},"TG God, Privilege of Seeing"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.3b","order":"06.05.130.16118"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/14.23.21-23"},"John 14:23 (21–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.1"},"D&C 93:1"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.3c","order":"06.05.130.16120"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.36"},"Alma 34:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.22"},"D&C 130:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.4a","order":"06.05.130.16122"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/3.9.4-10"},"Abr. 3:9 (4–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/4.13.13-14"},"4:13 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/5.13"},"5:13"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/time"},"TG Time"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.5a","order":"06.05.130.16124"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.5b","order":"06.05.130.16126"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.6"},"D&C 7:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.25"},"43:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/129.3.3,6-7"},"129:3 (3, 6–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.7a","order":"06.05.130.16128"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/18.10"},"Matt. 18:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/25.31"},"25:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/1.7"},"2 Thes. 1:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.21"},"D&C 76:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.37"},"136:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.7b","order":"06.05.130.16130"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/6.16"},"1 Tim. 6:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.62,94.94,119"},"D&C 76:62, 94 (94, 119)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.19"},"88:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.7c","order":"06.05.130.16132"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.4.4,26-28"},"Ezek. 1:4 (4, 26–28)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.23"},"Hel. 5:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.41"},"D&C 133:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/137.2"},"137:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.7d","order":"06.05.130.16134"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/4.6"},"Rev. 4:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/15.2.1-4"},"15:2 (1–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.7e","order":"06.05.130.16136"},["b","7e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/33.14"},"Isa. 33:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.8a","order":"06.05.130.16138"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/urim-and-thummim"},"TG Urim and Thummim"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.9a","order":"06.05.130.16140"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-destiny-of"},"TG Earth, Destiny of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.9b","order":"06.05.130.16142"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.1"},"D&C 77:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.9c","order":"06.05.130.16144"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/immortality"},"TG Immortality"],"."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.9d","order":"06.05.130.16146"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.22"},"Ezek. 1:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"9e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.9e","order":"06.05.130.16148"},["b","9e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-king"},"TG Jesus Christ, King"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.10a","order":"06.05.130.16150"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/urim-and-thummim"},"TG Urim and Thummim"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.10b","order":"06.05.130.16152"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/3.3.3-17"},"Abr. 3:3 (3–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.11a","order":"06.05.130.16154"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/2.17"},"Rev. 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.11b","order":"06.05.130.16156"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/62.2"},"Isa. 62:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.15"},"65:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/5.12.9-14"},"Mosiah 5:12 (9–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.12a","order":"06.05.130.16158"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.29"},"D&C 38:2